1
00:01:40,720 --> 00:01:46,030
[THE DEVIL BETWEEN US]

2
00:01:46,060 --> 00:01:48,920
[Episode 16]

3
00:01:57,070 --> 00:01:57,789
Move.

4
00:01:58,590 --> 00:01:59,850
I can't go any further.

5
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:02,860
The courtyard must be
crawling with cops right now.

6
00:02:13,890 --> 00:02:14,890
I'll go in for you.

7
00:02:16,670 --> 00:02:17,280
You don't know Xue.

8
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:18,680
What are you going in for?

9
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:19,770
Did you sign the surgery consent?

10
00:02:19,770 --> 00:02:20,770
Yeah, I signed it.

11
00:02:21,120 --> 00:02:22,310
Once you walk in there with the cash,

12
00:02:22,310 --> 00:02:23,710
there's no turning back.

13
00:02:24,010 --> 00:02:24,630
Think about it—

14
00:02:24,630 --> 00:02:26,400
if the police seize that money,

15
00:02:26,720 --> 00:02:27,780
what happens then?

16
00:02:28,970 --> 00:02:30,570
They can't do anything to me.

17
00:02:31,630 --> 00:02:33,400
I'll call you in a bit.

18
00:02:34,460 --> 00:02:35,410
I'll tell them

19
00:02:35,710 --> 00:02:36,370
you asked me

20
00:02:36,690 --> 00:02:37,840
to deliver the money

21
00:02:37,840 --> 00:02:39,310
to a guy named Xue.

22
00:02:40,210 --> 00:02:41,690
Once I hand it over, I'm out.

23
00:02:41,690 --> 00:02:42,900
After this is done,

24
00:02:43,450 --> 00:02:45,579
you're helping me with one more thing.

25
00:02:46,430 --> 00:02:47,320
Here, take the phone.

26
00:02:47,320 --> 00:02:47,920
Answer it.

27
00:03:47,520 --> 00:03:48,310
Officer Jin.

28
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:52,290
What are you doing here?

29
00:03:52,540 --> 00:03:54,800
I'm here to deliver money for my brother.

30
00:03:54,820 --> 00:03:55,510
What money?

31
00:03:56,220 --> 00:03:57,520
He said he owes someone

32
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:59,180
the fee for an organ donation.

33
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:02,850
Where is your brother?

34
00:04:03,320 --> 00:04:05,180
He's at the hospital with Jiajia.

35
00:04:06,080 --> 00:04:07,590
He just messaged me

36
00:04:07,620 --> 00:04:09,360
to bring the money
to the inpatient department

37
00:04:09,360 --> 00:04:10,960
and give it to a man named Xue.

38
00:04:11,700 --> 00:04:13,820
I just withdrew it from the bank.

39
00:04:16,230 --> 00:04:17,560
Okay. Xue is over there.

40
00:04:17,610 --> 00:04:18,360
I'll take you to him.

41
00:04:18,360 --> 00:04:18,959
Thank you.

42
00:04:20,430 --> 00:04:22,110
How much is in this bag?

43
00:04:22,440 --> 00:04:23,570
1,080,000 yuan in total.

44
00:04:23,570 --> 00:04:26,570
8,000 yuan is for Jiajia's
renewed hospital deposit.

45
00:04:26,820 --> 00:04:27,550
That's a lot.

46
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,000
As his brother,

47
00:04:29,000 --> 00:04:30,880
I've gotta help when he's in trouble.

48
00:04:30,880 --> 00:04:32,610
Where did you get so much money?

49
00:04:33,320 --> 00:04:35,390
Some I borrowed from friends,

50
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:38,680
and some Xiaoya and I earned
from our online business.

51
00:04:39,630 --> 00:04:40,300
Not easy.

52
00:04:41,640 --> 00:04:42,480
This is Xue.

53
00:04:45,460 --> 00:04:46,260
Xue.

54
00:04:47,510 --> 00:04:48,159
Hello.

55
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:49,600
I'm Cheng Ken's brother.

56
00:04:49,600 --> 00:04:51,460
He asked me to bring you the money.

57
00:04:51,950 --> 00:04:52,720
What money?

58
00:04:53,790 --> 00:04:54,920
That makes no sense.

59
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:55,980
My brother asked me

60
00:04:56,570 --> 00:04:59,100
to bring you 1,000,000 yuan.

61
00:04:59,130 --> 00:05:00,240
I just withdrew it from the bank.

62
00:05:00,240 --> 00:05:02,040
Cheng Xiaodong has arrived with the money.

63
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:03,440
Cheng Ken didn't show up.

64
00:05:03,790 --> 00:05:04,350
Tell him

65
00:05:04,370 --> 00:05:05,230
to take it back.

66
00:05:05,790 --> 00:05:06,590
Wait, what?

67
00:05:07,330 --> 00:05:08,570
Take the money back.

68
00:05:08,680 --> 00:05:09,560
Xue,

69
00:05:10,920 --> 00:05:12,520
do you think it's not enough?

70
00:05:12,720 --> 00:05:14,310
Xue, it's 1,000,000 yuan.

71
00:05:14,490 --> 00:05:15,750
You can do a lot with it.

72
00:05:15,990 --> 00:05:17,450
Go back and tell Cheng Ken,

73
00:05:17,760 --> 00:05:20,090
I never intended to sell my son.

74
00:05:20,790 --> 00:05:22,150
Are you regretting it?

75
00:05:23,070 --> 00:05:23,750
If he doesn't get treatment now,

76
00:05:23,750 --> 00:05:24,830
it will be too late.

77
00:05:44,440 --> 00:05:47,780
[China Organ Donation Registration Form]

78
00:05:46,430 --> 00:05:47,070
This is a copy of Jiang's

79
00:05:47,070 --> 00:05:49,360
body donation consent.

80
00:05:52,280 --> 00:05:55,280
All his organs have been donated to
medical institutions—

81
00:05:55,280 --> 00:05:56,810
completely free of charge.

82
00:06:04,010 --> 00:06:05,660
We signed it a long time ago.

83
00:06:07,700 --> 00:06:09,220
It was Jiang's own wish.

84
00:06:14,070 --> 00:06:16,230
My son begged us to sign.

85
00:06:18,670 --> 00:06:20,510
I want to leave my body

86
00:06:24,120 --> 00:06:25,510
to Jiajia

87
00:06:28,460 --> 00:06:30,190
and to anyone who needs it.

88
00:06:33,560 --> 00:06:34,159
This

89
00:06:36,630 --> 00:06:38,310
is my final

90
00:06:39,740 --> 00:06:40,620
wish.

91
00:06:44,540 --> 00:06:47,210
We never intended to take any money.

92
00:06:49,080 --> 00:06:51,270
The only reason I agreed to sign

93
00:06:51,980 --> 00:06:54,330
was to honor my son's wish

94
00:06:55,060 --> 00:06:56,790
to donate his kidney to Jiajia.

95
00:06:57,190 --> 00:06:58,990
As for one million, two million…

96
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:01,840
that was all Cheng Ken's wishful thinking.

97
00:07:13,770 --> 00:07:15,250
This has gone way too far.

98
00:07:15,970 --> 00:07:17,300
What do you mean, a joke?

99
00:07:19,470 --> 00:07:21,600
I just want his daughter to get better.

100
00:07:22,390 --> 00:07:23,680
Who's joking with him?

101
00:07:24,490 --> 00:07:27,090
Does what he thinks
have anything to do with me?

102
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:38,870
Ken,

103
00:07:40,770 --> 00:07:42,900
the price you've paid is just too high.

104
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:49,250
Why didn't he say so sooner?

105
00:08:03,790 --> 00:08:05,440
Why didn't he say so sooner?

106
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:08,430
Why?

107
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:11,370
You came alone?

108
00:09:11,370 --> 00:09:11,940
Yes.

109
00:09:13,670 --> 00:09:14,840
Cheng Ken didn't show up?

110
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:16,030
Over a million in cash.

111
00:09:16,030 --> 00:09:16,960
That money isn't Cheng Xiaodong's.

112
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,070
He doesn't have that kind of cash.

113
00:09:18,070 --> 00:09:19,070
It's Li Xiaoya's.

114
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:21,000
And there's no way she'd use her own money

115
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,430
for his relatives.

116
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:35,270
There has to be some kind of
vested interest

117
00:09:35,270 --> 00:09:36,580
between her and Cheng Ken.

118
00:09:36,580 --> 00:09:39,090
What kind of interest
could they possibly have?

119
00:09:39,090 --> 00:09:40,750
It's gotta be about the drugs.

120
00:09:40,910 --> 00:09:41,870
What do you mean?

121
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,840
Didn't you look into
those diet pills?

122
00:09:44,840 --> 00:09:45,550
Didn't they check out?

123
00:09:45,550 --> 00:09:46,240
They were clean.

124
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:47,270
We've been tailing Cheng Ken
the whole time, right?

125
00:09:47,270 --> 00:09:48,240
Nothing came up.

126
00:09:48,840 --> 00:09:49,670
So what's the problem now?

127
00:09:49,670 --> 00:09:50,480
I'm stumped.

128
00:09:54,440 --> 00:09:55,900
I'm going to see Li Xiaoya.

129
00:09:56,630 --> 00:09:58,490
Time to lay our cards on the table.

130
00:09:59,150 --> 00:10:00,440
I'll tell Tan Jie to come back you up.

131
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,240
Don't stare at him.

132
00:10:01,240 --> 00:10:02,360
Play on your phone or something.

133
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:03,840
You look exactly like a cop.

134
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:04,360
Okay.

135
00:10:12,270 --> 00:10:12,800
Wenjing,

136
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:14,870
Cheng Xiaodong booked two tickets to Maide

137
00:10:14,870 --> 00:10:16,030
four days ago.

138
00:10:16,030 --> 00:10:18,760
The passengers
are Li Xiaoya and Cheng Xiaodong.

139
00:10:18,810 --> 00:10:19,670
Got it.

140
00:10:27,480 --> 00:10:28,240
Tan Jie.

141
00:10:28,670 --> 00:10:29,000
Wenjing.

142
00:10:29,000 --> 00:10:30,240
Head to the hospital

143
00:10:30,240 --> 00:10:31,770
and support Jin Longzheng.

144
00:10:31,840 --> 00:10:33,510
Until I get solid evidence, keep your eyes
on Cheng Xiaodong.

145
00:10:33,510 --> 00:10:35,010
Don't let him out of your sight.

146
00:10:35,010 --> 00:10:35,510
On it.

147
00:10:58,020 --> 00:10:58,900
Li Xiaoya!

148
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:01,630
Li Xiaoya!

149
00:11:02,930 --> 00:11:03,760
Li Xiaoya!

150
00:11:04,480 --> 00:11:05,150
Wenjing!

151
00:11:05,660 --> 00:11:06,300
Wenjing!

152
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,600
Xiaoya has already left.

153
00:11:10,460 --> 00:11:11,520
When did she leave?

154
00:11:12,170 --> 00:11:13,650
Probably this morning.

155
00:11:14,150 --> 00:11:15,120
She originally told me

156
00:11:15,120 --> 00:11:16,720
to start shipping tomorrow,

157
00:11:16,910 --> 00:11:18,000
but she came by early today and said

158
00:11:18,000 --> 00:11:19,150
I could start now.

159
00:11:20,910 --> 00:11:21,840
Where did she go?

160
00:11:24,670 --> 00:11:26,070
After what she did,

161
00:11:27,080 --> 00:11:28,680
there's no way she'd tell me.

162
00:11:29,490 --> 00:11:30,840
But when she was arguing with
Cheng Xiaodong,

163
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:32,370
I heard them mention a boat.

164
00:11:36,140 --> 00:11:37,520
So do you know what she did?

165
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:38,250
Do you know?

166
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:58,350
When I touched this white stuff,

167
00:11:59,970 --> 00:12:01,430
I knew what was inside.

168
00:12:04,860 --> 00:12:06,460
I thought about it all night.

169
00:12:08,670 --> 00:12:09,840
On one side it's you,

170
00:12:11,370 --> 00:12:12,770
on the other it's Xiaoya.

171
00:12:14,400 --> 00:12:16,270
I didn't know what to do.

172
00:12:18,890 --> 00:12:20,560
I know Xiaoya was wrong.

173
00:12:21,510 --> 00:12:23,600
I don't want more people
ending up like me,

174
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,840
letting this stuff

175
00:12:26,360 --> 00:12:28,390
ruin their lives.

176
00:12:41,160 --> 00:12:41,920
Let's go.

177
00:12:49,580 --> 00:12:52,000
[Operating Patient Entrance]

178
00:12:56,750 --> 00:12:58,010
Alright, Officer Jin.

179
00:12:58,420 --> 00:13:00,140
I just deposited 80,000 yuan

180
00:13:00,440 --> 00:13:02,240
for Jiajia's hospital deposit.

181
00:13:02,350 --> 00:13:04,210
Since Xue doesn't want the money,

182
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:06,570
I have to put it back in the bank.

183
00:13:06,630 --> 00:13:07,360
I'll be off now.

184
00:13:07,360 --> 00:13:08,290
I won't keep you.

185
00:13:08,560 --> 00:13:09,490
I'll go with you.

186
00:13:16,550 --> 00:13:17,480
You just do your work.

187
00:13:17,480 --> 00:13:18,600
I can go by myself.

188
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:19,380
It's fine.

189
00:13:19,460 --> 00:13:20,620
I'll go with you.

190
00:13:20,840 --> 00:13:22,200
Carrying all that cash alone

191
00:13:22,200 --> 00:13:23,660
isn't safe on the streets.

192
00:13:26,310 --> 00:13:26,950
Exactly.

193
00:13:27,670 --> 00:13:29,840
It isn't safe for me
to carry so much money.

194
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:30,830
If you come with me,

195
00:13:30,830 --> 00:13:31,490
I'll feel safer.

196
00:13:31,490 --> 00:13:32,010
Right?

197
00:13:40,760 --> 00:13:41,760
After you.

198
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:08,790
We found the evidence.

199
00:14:08,790 --> 00:14:10,490
Prepare to arrest Cheng Xiaodong.

200
00:14:10,490 --> 00:14:11,010
Got it.

201
00:14:45,430 --> 00:14:46,100
Let's go!

202
00:14:47,320 --> 00:14:48,080
Get up!

203
00:14:49,580 --> 00:14:51,640
If we don't leave now, we're done for!

204
00:14:58,920 --> 00:14:59,830
Cheng Ken!

205
00:15:00,240 --> 00:15:01,150
Cheng Ken!

206
00:15:15,100 --> 00:15:17,390
He ran out the back door of the hospital.

207
00:15:17,700 --> 00:15:18,430
Cheng Ken...

208
00:15:18,750 --> 00:15:19,950
Cheng Ken is with him.

209
00:15:20,280 --> 00:15:21,720
A black Toyota Camry.

210
00:15:21,910 --> 00:15:22,840
I didn't catch the plate number.

211
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:24,640
I didn't catch the plate number.

212
00:15:59,720 --> 00:16:01,150
My colleague
is waiting for you at the station.

213
00:16:01,150 --> 00:16:01,990
You can explain it, right?

214
00:16:01,990 --> 00:16:02,530
Yes.

215
00:16:02,810 --> 00:16:04,870
Talk things over when you see Xiaoya.

216
00:16:05,190 --> 00:16:06,120
Be safe.

217
00:16:06,150 --> 00:16:06,480
I know.

218
00:16:06,480 --> 00:16:07,540
I have to find her first.

219
00:16:07,540 --> 00:16:08,400
Hurry up and go.

220
00:16:10,140 --> 00:16:11,100
Drive safely.

221
00:16:27,400 --> 00:16:28,200
Director Dai.

222
00:16:28,420 --> 00:16:28,950
Go ahead.

223
00:16:29,340 --> 00:16:31,670
There are drugs in Li Xiaoya's diet pills.

224
00:16:31,700 --> 00:16:32,930
I've already had Wang Ping

225
00:16:32,930 --> 00:16:34,530
take the pills to the bureau.

226
00:16:34,950 --> 00:16:36,600
Shouldn't we track down a few more people—

227
00:16:36,600 --> 00:16:38,030
the ones who bought the first batch

228
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:39,320
from Li Xiaoya's circle—

229
00:16:39,320 --> 00:16:40,920
and have their blood tested?

230
00:16:41,150 --> 00:16:41,950
Leave it to me.

231
00:16:42,750 --> 00:16:44,010
Where is Li Xiaoya now?

232
00:16:44,340 --> 00:16:44,870
The plane ticket...

233
00:16:44,870 --> 00:16:46,120
I suspect it's

234
00:16:46,120 --> 00:16:47,600
just a cover.

235
00:16:48,860 --> 00:16:51,120
I think she's already headed to the pier.

236
00:16:51,270 --> 00:16:52,440
I'm on my way there.

237
00:16:52,950 --> 00:16:54,600
She might be trying to escape by boat.

238
00:16:54,600 --> 00:16:55,630
The pier?

239
00:16:56,840 --> 00:16:59,100
Then I need to call the coast guard
to back you up.

240
00:16:59,100 --> 00:16:59,790
You can't handle both piers

241
00:16:59,790 --> 00:17:00,750
alone.

242
00:17:01,150 --> 00:17:02,630
I'll have Zhang Yan
and his team support you.

243
00:17:02,630 --> 00:17:03,080
Okay.

244
00:17:03,480 --> 00:17:03,910
Also,

245
00:17:04,349 --> 00:17:06,670
I'll get people to check

246
00:17:06,690 --> 00:17:08,400
if Li Xiaoya has any other places
she might be hiding,

247
00:17:08,400 --> 00:17:09,270
see if there's anything.

248
00:17:09,270 --> 00:17:10,240
Director Dai,

249
00:17:10,240 --> 00:17:11,160
um...

250
00:17:12,640 --> 00:17:13,200
Wang Ping.

251
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:14,859
Have Wang Ping tested as well.

252
00:17:15,310 --> 00:17:16,040
Don't worry.

253
00:17:16,750 --> 00:17:17,400
Stay safe.

254
00:17:17,640 --> 00:17:18,230
Will do.

255
00:17:31,030 --> 00:17:31,720
Sir.

256
00:17:32,000 --> 00:17:32,590
Sir.

257
00:17:33,010 --> 00:17:35,140
Can you take me out for a ride on the sea?

258
00:17:35,240 --> 00:17:37,020
No can do. This boat
doesn't take passengers.

259
00:17:37,020 --> 00:17:38,150
Just a quick spin.

260
00:17:38,170 --> 00:17:39,900
I'll give you 1,000 yuan, okay?

261
00:17:40,030 --> 00:17:41,350
Bring me back by two.

262
00:17:42,810 --> 00:17:43,610
1,500 yuan.

263
00:17:43,960 --> 00:17:44,470
I'll give you 2,000 yuan.

264
00:17:44,470 --> 00:17:44,950
Hurry.

265
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:58,240
Xiaoyu has to die.

266
00:18:03,400 --> 00:18:05,400
Can't you just leave her somewhere?

267
00:18:06,660 --> 00:18:07,870
She's a fool.

268
00:18:08,960 --> 00:18:09,890
She won't talk.

269
00:18:11,000 --> 00:18:13,130
We've destroyed most of the evidence.

270
00:18:13,750 --> 00:18:15,200
Even if the cops catch us,

271
00:18:16,540 --> 00:18:18,300
those few tainted diet pills

272
00:18:19,270 --> 00:18:20,870
would only get us a few years.

273
00:18:21,400 --> 00:18:22,830
But if Xiaoyu lives,

274
00:18:23,410 --> 00:18:24,160
she can prove

275
00:18:24,160 --> 00:18:25,590
all the drugs are ours.

276
00:18:26,490 --> 00:18:27,490
She has to die.

277
00:18:27,790 --> 00:18:28,790
That's the only way

278
00:18:28,790 --> 00:18:29,830
we survive.

279
00:18:33,000 --> 00:18:34,720
Isn't killing a crime?

280
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:35,930
Let's make a bet.

281
00:18:36,680 --> 00:18:38,810
Don't you and Li Xiaoya love to gamble?

282
00:18:43,590 --> 00:18:44,550
Cheng Ken,

283
00:18:46,030 --> 00:18:47,310
we are drug dealers.

284
00:18:48,160 --> 00:18:48,550
In just these few days,

285
00:18:48,550 --> 00:18:50,350
look how many people we've hurt.

286
00:18:50,550 --> 00:18:51,810
We are not good people.

287
00:18:52,310 --> 00:18:54,070
We have no conscience left!

288
00:19:07,790 --> 00:19:10,050
Stop at the shop at the village entrance.

289
00:19:11,790 --> 00:19:13,720
I want to buy something for Xiaoyu.

290
00:19:19,860 --> 00:19:20,720
Is that it up ahead?

291
00:19:20,720 --> 00:19:22,180
The one parked by the road?

292
00:19:22,230 --> 00:19:22,990
No.

293
00:19:23,020 --> 00:19:23,830
It's a black one.

294
00:19:23,830 --> 00:19:25,110
Black Toyota Camry.

295
00:19:30,830 --> 00:19:31,590
Director Dai.

296
00:19:31,590 --> 00:19:32,400
You and Tan Jie

297
00:19:32,820 --> 00:19:34,680
head to Li Xiaoya's old house now.

298
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:36,970
Cheng Ken and Cheng Xiaodong

299
00:19:36,970 --> 00:19:38,630
might go there to look for her.

300
00:19:39,030 --> 00:19:40,890
I'm sending you the location now.

301
00:19:41,240 --> 00:19:41,680
Okay.

302
00:19:41,830 --> 00:19:43,560
Okay. We're heading there now.

303
00:19:54,550 --> 00:19:55,200
Hello, comrade.

304
00:19:55,200 --> 00:19:55,640
Hi.

305
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:56,270
Director Dai said

306
00:19:56,270 --> 00:19:57,200
the boats are ready.

307
00:19:57,200 --> 00:19:57,550
Okay.

308
00:19:57,880 --> 00:19:58,440
Listen.

309
00:19:58,550 --> 00:19:59,960
You two take that boat.

310
00:19:59,980 --> 00:20:02,110
The rest of you come with me to this one.

311
00:20:07,590 --> 00:20:08,590
Have you checked?

312
00:20:09,230 --> 00:20:09,550
Have you checked?

313
00:20:09,550 --> 00:20:10,000
We've checked everything.

314
00:20:10,000 --> 00:20:10,720
Nothing.

315
00:20:10,920 --> 00:20:11,750
Then let's check

316
00:20:11,750 --> 00:20:13,480
all the medium-to-large boats

317
00:20:13,600 --> 00:20:14,590
that filed sea departure
reports this morning.

318
00:20:14,590 --> 00:20:15,960
Any boat over 12 meters

319
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:16,920
has to report.

320
00:20:17,210 --> 00:20:18,230
So far, no problems.

321
00:20:18,230 --> 00:20:18,880
Okay.

322
00:20:18,910 --> 00:20:20,970
How about I get on
your coast guard boat first?

323
00:20:20,970 --> 00:20:22,200
We can search nearby

324
00:20:22,200 --> 00:20:24,860
and see if there are
any suspicious small boats.

325
00:20:29,550 --> 00:20:30,150
Wenjing.

326
00:20:30,830 --> 00:20:32,070
How's it going on your end?

327
00:20:32,070 --> 00:20:32,830
I just checked

328
00:20:32,830 --> 00:20:34,440
all the medium-to-large boats'
departure reports—

329
00:20:34,440 --> 00:20:35,440
nothing unusual.

330
00:20:35,580 --> 00:20:37,840
We've already started searching at sea.

331
00:20:37,980 --> 00:20:38,490
Okay.

332
00:21:05,370 --> 00:21:06,000
Auntie.

333
00:21:06,370 --> 00:21:06,920
You should go back.

334
00:21:06,920 --> 00:21:07,910
We're busy here.

335
00:21:11,730 --> 00:21:12,620
Let me.

336
00:21:12,920 --> 00:21:13,600
Go ahead.

337
00:21:25,990 --> 00:21:26,670
Let's go.

338
00:21:31,140 --> 00:21:31,820
Let's go.

339
00:21:45,520 --> 00:21:46,270
Let's do this.

340
00:21:46,270 --> 00:21:48,550
We'll follow this mountain

341
00:21:48,780 --> 00:21:49,950
and go around. Okay?

342
00:21:49,970 --> 00:21:50,530
Okay.

343
00:21:54,790 --> 00:21:57,040
Can we stay further away
from the coastline?

344
00:21:57,040 --> 00:21:57,770
Is that okay?

345
00:21:58,090 --> 00:21:58,650
Okay.

346
00:22:23,630 --> 00:22:24,240
I'm going upstairs.

347
00:22:24,240 --> 00:22:24,830
Go up.

348
00:22:29,840 --> 00:22:30,440
Anything?

349
00:22:30,460 --> 00:22:30,990
Nothing.

350
00:22:33,690 --> 00:22:34,410
Who are you?

351
00:22:34,600 --> 00:22:35,860
Why are you in my house?

352
00:22:36,880 --> 00:22:37,880
We're the police.

353
00:22:40,110 --> 00:22:41,440
Is something wrong?

354
00:23:11,150 --> 00:23:12,910
Dad, what's wrong?

355
00:23:14,600 --> 00:23:15,600
I'm just thinking

356
00:23:17,200 --> 00:23:19,260
that doing bad things is really hard.

357
00:23:20,920 --> 00:23:22,830
Aren't we good people?

358
00:23:23,110 --> 00:23:25,200
Why do we have to do bad things?

359
00:23:27,400 --> 00:23:28,960
About Xiaoyu…

360
00:23:29,220 --> 00:23:30,500
I still promise you:

361
00:23:30,700 --> 00:23:32,550
once I handle all the problems

362
00:23:32,550 --> 00:23:33,610
and earn the money,

363
00:23:34,350 --> 00:23:35,500
I'll bring you along

364
00:23:35,520 --> 00:23:36,720
to be with Xiaoyu.

365
00:23:36,750 --> 00:23:37,880
We'll go somewhere

366
00:23:38,200 --> 00:23:39,470
new

367
00:23:40,310 --> 00:23:41,710
and live properly.

368
00:23:42,710 --> 00:23:44,770
Xiaoyu is a benefactor to our family.

369
00:23:45,220 --> 00:23:46,870
We'll always treat her well.

370
00:23:48,140 --> 00:23:49,690
Xiaoyu, if you're scared,

371
00:23:49,720 --> 00:23:51,700
just think of her as Jiajia.

372
00:23:51,810 --> 00:23:53,850
I'll be with you the whole time.

373
00:23:59,190 --> 00:23:59,840
Jiajia,

374
00:23:59,960 --> 00:24:01,380
if you had to

375
00:24:01,710 --> 00:24:04,440
choose between Dad and Xiaoyu,

376
00:24:04,840 --> 00:24:05,990
who would you pick?

377
00:24:06,360 --> 00:24:07,960
I'd definitely pick you.

378
00:24:07,980 --> 00:24:09,700
But I don't want to choose.

379
00:24:13,470 --> 00:24:14,800
Xiaodong, stop the car.

380
00:24:16,270 --> 00:24:17,670
There's a grove up ahead.

381
00:24:17,750 --> 00:24:19,230
Let's talk when we get there.

382
00:24:19,230 --> 00:24:19,960
Stop the car.

383
00:24:19,960 --> 00:24:21,000
I said we'll talk when we get there!

384
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:21,790
Stop the car!

385
00:24:22,230 --> 00:24:22,960
Stop!

386
00:24:24,660 --> 00:24:25,380
Stop!

387
00:24:29,200 --> 00:24:30,000
Are you crazy?

388
00:24:38,360 --> 00:24:39,030
Get out.

389
00:24:48,950 --> 00:24:49,670
I'll drive.

390
00:25:07,270 --> 00:25:08,000
Run!

391
00:25:09,240 --> 00:25:09,840
Run!

392
00:25:10,200 --> 00:25:10,830
Run!

393
00:25:11,480 --> 00:25:12,270
Run!

394
00:25:12,650 --> 00:25:13,170
Run!

395
00:25:13,240 --> 00:25:14,040
You're crazy!

396
00:25:14,720 --> 00:25:15,400
Run!

397
00:25:15,420 --> 00:25:16,150
Give it to me!

398
00:25:20,960 --> 00:25:21,400
Go!

399
00:25:25,400 --> 00:25:26,030
Run!

400
00:25:27,000 --> 00:25:27,550
Run!

401
00:25:27,550 --> 00:25:28,240
Xiaoyu!

402
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:29,400
Run!

403
00:25:35,960 --> 00:25:36,990
Don't stop me!

404
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:40,070
Run!

405
00:25:40,880 --> 00:25:41,460
Run!

406
00:25:41,480 --> 00:25:42,000
Let go!

407
00:25:42,070 --> 00:25:43,160
Run!

408
00:25:43,590 --> 00:25:44,350
Let go!

409
00:25:44,640 --> 00:25:45,590
Run!

410
00:25:45,830 --> 00:25:46,480
Let go!

411
00:26:31,550 --> 00:26:32,600
Is that her?

412
00:26:33,400 --> 00:26:34,880
Does that one look like her?

413
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:35,920
Go over there.

414
00:26:43,270 --> 00:26:44,130
That's the car!

415
00:26:44,370 --> 00:26:44,960
Intercept it.

416
00:26:44,960 --> 00:26:45,370
Hurry up.

417
00:26:45,370 --> 00:26:45,770
Okay.

418
00:27:45,030 --> 00:27:45,960
Cheng Xiaodong!

419
00:27:47,840 --> 00:27:48,770
Cheng Xiaodong!

420
00:27:48,960 --> 00:27:49,960
Cheng Xiaodong!

421
00:27:50,110 --> 00:27:51,110
Gunshot warning!

422
00:27:55,600 --> 00:27:56,640
Cheng Xiaodong!

423
00:28:41,220 --> 00:28:42,230
Where is Cheng Ken?

424
00:28:42,230 --> 00:28:43,110
Where is Cheng Ken?

425
00:28:43,110 --> 00:28:44,190
Where is Cheng Ken?

426
00:28:47,570 --> 00:28:48,630
Where is Cheng Ken?

427
00:29:21,380 --> 00:29:22,240
How is it going?

428
00:29:22,580 --> 00:29:23,380
Where are you?

429
00:29:24,910 --> 00:29:25,720
Li Xiaoya.

430
00:29:28,840 --> 00:29:29,640
Li Xiaoya.

431
00:29:36,620 --> 00:29:37,380
Li Xiaoya.

432
00:29:38,110 --> 00:29:39,780
Can you hear me, Li Xiaoya?

433
00:30:37,180 --> 00:30:37,910
Hu Wenjing.

434
00:30:39,030 --> 00:30:40,790
Li Xiaoya is using a new number.

435
00:30:41,560 --> 00:30:43,220
I just confirmed with the telecom company—

436
00:30:43,220 --> 00:30:44,480
the last connection

437
00:30:44,510 --> 00:30:46,270
was at the Lingzhou pier tower.

438
00:30:46,640 --> 00:30:47,160
Okay.

439
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:48,690
What's your situation now?

440
00:30:49,260 --> 00:30:50,750
We found the girl from the hotel.

441
00:30:50,750 --> 00:30:52,530
She has intellectual disabilities.

442
00:30:52,530 --> 00:30:53,580
No wonder.

443
00:30:56,760 --> 00:30:58,220
Cheng Ken has been caught,

444
00:30:58,440 --> 00:30:59,970
but Cheng Xiaodong is dead.

445
00:31:01,700 --> 00:31:02,530
Okay, I got it.

446
00:31:03,200 --> 00:31:05,640
We're heading to Lingzhou Pier now.

447
00:31:21,830 --> 00:31:22,830
Can you hurry up?

448
00:31:23,410 --> 00:31:24,610
When will you arrive?

449
00:31:25,590 --> 00:31:27,030
Can I board from the sea?

450
00:31:27,620 --> 00:31:28,420
Yes, yes, yes.

451
00:31:28,780 --> 00:31:30,180
I'm not going to the pier.

452
00:31:31,100 --> 00:31:32,360
All units, attention.

453
00:31:32,510 --> 00:31:34,510
Vessel 00772, emergency report.

454
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:35,880
Target located:

455
00:31:35,900 --> 00:31:37,450
a blue fishing boat

456
00:31:37,480 --> 00:31:38,380
with three people,

457
00:31:38,380 --> 00:31:39,580
heading 176°

458
00:31:39,610 --> 00:31:40,970
at 15 knots,

459
00:31:40,990 --> 00:31:42,200
fleeing south.

460
00:31:42,230 --> 00:31:45,560
Request Vessel 20583
to intercept from the south,

461
00:31:45,790 --> 00:31:48,640
Vessel 33019 to encircle
from the southwest.

462
00:31:48,980 --> 00:31:50,040
Stop your boat ahead!

463
00:31:50,040 --> 00:31:51,550
We are the Chinese Coast Guard.

464
00:31:51,550 --> 00:31:54,010
Stop immediately and submit to inspection.

465
00:31:55,510 --> 00:31:56,590
Stop your boat at once!

466
00:31:56,590 --> 00:31:57,310
Hurry!

467
00:31:59,740 --> 00:32:00,540
Stop the boat.

468
00:32:24,790 --> 00:32:25,470
Wenjing.

469
00:32:26,650 --> 00:32:27,400
Come back with me.

470
00:32:27,400 --> 00:32:28,800
What are you doing there?

471
00:32:30,620 --> 00:32:32,140
On the last day of my life,

472
00:32:34,470 --> 00:32:36,320
I'm actually kind of happy

473
00:32:36,990 --> 00:32:38,560
to have a friend like you to see me off.

474
00:32:38,560 --> 00:32:39,910
Why the last day?

475
00:32:40,720 --> 00:32:41,240
No one is seeing you off.

476
00:32:41,240 --> 00:32:41,920
I'm here to pick you up.

477
00:32:41,920 --> 00:32:42,370
Hurry up.

478
00:32:42,370 --> 00:32:43,430
Come over here now.

479
00:32:43,490 --> 00:32:45,490
You're messing with me, Hu Wenjing.

480
00:32:48,790 --> 00:32:50,160
Do I look like

481
00:32:50,390 --> 00:32:52,050
a complete failure right now?

482
00:32:55,790 --> 00:32:58,070
This isn't how I imagined it would end.

483
00:33:00,440 --> 00:33:01,650
It's fine. Let it be.

484
00:33:03,660 --> 00:33:04,910
Let it end here.

485
00:33:05,670 --> 00:33:07,970
Li Xiaoya, ending it here is pathetic.

486
00:33:08,020 --> 00:33:10,220
And how's it supposed to look "decent"?

487
00:33:12,580 --> 00:33:14,380
I've long since lost all of that.

488
00:33:15,920 --> 00:33:17,670
I'm not like you or Wang Ping—

489
00:33:18,350 --> 00:33:19,550
you two can put yourselves out there

490
00:33:19,550 --> 00:33:20,960
for others to see.

491
00:33:22,120 --> 00:33:22,950
I can't.

492
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:28,040
My whole life's been a vanity show,

493
00:33:29,820 --> 00:33:30,770
and I accept it.

494
00:33:33,680 --> 00:33:34,480
Wenjing,

495
00:33:37,590 --> 00:33:39,070
leave me a little dignity.

496
00:33:40,410 --> 00:33:41,940
I'm not going back with you.

497
00:33:43,680 --> 00:33:44,890
As for Wang Ping,

498
00:33:45,620 --> 00:33:46,720
you take care of her.

499
00:33:46,720 --> 00:33:47,440
I can't.

500
00:33:47,650 --> 00:33:49,580
I can't handle Wang Ping by myself.

501
00:33:49,700 --> 00:33:50,700
Come over here now.

502
00:33:50,700 --> 00:33:52,560
What's so scary about going home?

503
00:33:53,120 --> 00:33:53,600
Hurry!

504
00:33:56,200 --> 00:33:57,030
Hu Wenjing,

505
00:34:00,550 --> 00:34:02,030
you're an average friend.

506
00:34:04,030 --> 00:34:04,960
In the next life,

507
00:34:06,280 --> 00:34:07,890
I'll give you another chance

508
00:34:09,280 --> 00:34:10,340
to prove yourself.

509
00:34:25,889 --> 00:34:26,659
Li Xiaoya!

510
00:34:33,810 --> 00:34:34,639
Wenjing!

511
00:34:35,440 --> 00:34:36,710
Skipper, full speed ahead!

512
00:34:36,710 --> 00:34:37,110
Hurry!

513
00:35:51,530 --> 00:35:53,110
[With the conclusion of the police operation,
the suspects, including Cheng Ken and Li Xiaoya,

514
00:35:53,110 --> 00:35:54,690
were arrested for multiple charges,]

515
00:35:54,710 --> 00:35:57,870
including illegal possession of drugs
and trafficking drugs.]

516
00:36:04,070 --> 00:36:05,600
[During the investigation, the police,
acting on Cheng Ken's confession,

517
00:36:05,600 --> 00:36:07,140
successfully recovered
the body of Cao Jinchuan.]

518
00:36:08,750 --> 00:36:11,020
[Han Qiang was brought to justice
for illegal possession of drugs and inciting others to use drugs.]

519
00:36:11,050 --> 00:36:13,570
[At the same time, Xiaoyu, who lacked criminal capacity, was rescued by the police and has been properly placed while awaiting contact from her family.]

520
00:36:13,600 --> 00:36:16,120
[The case has now entered the judicial process,
and all involved parties will face legal trial.]

521
00:36:16,140 --> 00:36:18,440
[The net of justice is vast and far-reaching;
wrongdoing will inevitably pay the price for its actions.]

522
00:36:23,190 --> 00:36:24,150
To date,

523
00:36:24,480 --> 00:36:27,040
China has placed 508 narcotic

524
00:36:27,570 --> 00:36:29,590
and psychotropic substances
under strict control,

525
00:36:29,590 --> 00:36:31,670
making us the nation
with the most heavily regulated drugs

526
00:36:31,670 --> 00:36:33,150
in the world.

527
00:36:33,780 --> 00:36:36,300
Yet new drugs continue to emerge,

528
00:36:37,070 --> 00:36:40,470
with more than a dozen added to
the controlled list each year.

529
00:36:40,530 --> 00:36:42,340
We can never afford to stop,

530
00:36:42,990 --> 00:36:45,400
never allow even the slightest slack.

531
00:36:45,670 --> 00:36:49,200
I am willing to dedicate my life
to the cause of drug prevention.

532
00:37:00,620 --> 00:37:03,950
Now, let us welcome Comrade Hu Wenjing
to the stage to speak.

533
00:38:00,820 --> 00:38:01,530
Mr. Yang.

534
00:38:03,440 --> 00:38:04,880
You are Hu Ming and Hu Zhi's mother,
right?

535
00:38:04,880 --> 00:38:05,710
Yes, I am.

536
00:38:06,790 --> 00:38:07,540
Take a look.

537
00:38:08,560 --> 00:38:09,190
I saw it.

538
00:38:09,190 --> 00:38:10,110
I just saw it at the entrance.

539
00:38:10,110 --> 00:38:10,990
I'm sorry.

540
00:38:11,820 --> 00:38:13,030
I've been teaching for so many years,

541
00:38:13,030 --> 00:38:14,630
and I've never run into
students like them.

542
00:38:14,630 --> 00:38:15,280
I...

543
00:38:15,280 --> 00:38:16,110
It's our fault.

544
00:38:16,110 --> 00:38:17,760
I'll deal with them when we get home.

545
00:38:17,760 --> 00:38:18,650
Sorry for the trouble.

546
00:38:18,650 --> 00:38:20,400
Let's talk later if you're free.

547
00:38:20,400 --> 00:38:20,880
I'm free.

548
00:38:20,880 --> 00:38:22,220
I'll take them to wash up first.

549
00:38:22,220 --> 00:38:22,860
Go ahead.

550
00:38:23,070 --> 00:38:23,880
Sorry.

551
00:38:25,280 --> 00:38:26,070
Come here.

552
00:38:26,440 --> 00:38:27,030
Let's go.

553
00:38:27,660 --> 00:38:28,770
Where is the restroom?

554
00:38:28,770 --> 00:38:29,320
I don't know.

555
00:38:29,320 --> 00:38:30,580
Where is the restroom?

556
00:38:34,070 --> 00:38:35,920
You two have no shame.

557
00:38:36,230 --> 00:38:38,090
Why did you smear it on your faces?

558
00:38:38,110 --> 00:38:38,960
Why?

559
00:38:39,710 --> 00:38:40,670
Bye.

560
00:38:41,380 --> 00:38:43,690
Is ink meant for your faces?

561
00:38:44,230 --> 00:38:45,000
Bye.

562
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:46,000
Thank you.

563
00:38:46,110 --> 00:38:46,960
Thank you.

564
00:38:47,710 --> 00:38:48,360
If this happens again,

565
00:38:48,360 --> 00:38:49,440
you two just wait.

566
00:38:50,230 --> 00:38:51,630
If this happens again...

567
00:38:51,630 --> 00:38:52,670
You seem free.

568
00:38:52,930 --> 00:38:54,450
You've got some nerve.

569
00:38:54,480 --> 00:38:56,440
You actually slipped
out of the department briefing?

570
00:38:56,440 --> 00:38:58,570
Do you even want that promotion or not?

571
00:38:59,060 --> 00:39:00,060
Where's your car?

572
00:39:00,190 --> 00:39:00,860
I didn't drive.

573
00:39:00,860 --> 00:39:02,720
I haven't figured out dinner yet.

574
00:39:02,880 --> 00:39:04,740
Are you here to mooch a meal again?

575
00:39:11,590 --> 00:39:12,070
